      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "AKII ROYALE (1) was strongly fancied and drifted back but wound up hard to hit the frame, 2.25 lengths from the winner (18.84) at Richmond in Maiden. Form from his last run is proving strong. Deserves serious consideration. ADRIFT (6) returned a better run last time, finishing in the money (18.04) at this track behind Kalimera in a Maiden. Has the pace to be prominent. Some good form is emerging from his last run. Expected to be in this for a long way. MELLCAT EXPRESS (7) was safely held on debut after settling well back when seventh (18.58) at this track over 324m. Can find the frame this time. GREENGROCER TOM (3) makes debut for the Dean Maniaci kennel. Profiles nicely and can feature in the finish.",
